##      factor  level .
df$ <- fct_relevel(df$, '', '', '')

df.extragt <- df |>
  ## df   
  group_by(, ) |>
  ##  ( 100 ) 
  filter(sum(_) > 100) |>
  ##  _, __, __, __    
  summarise_at(vars(_, __, __, __), funs(sum, mean)) |>
  ##      
  ungroup() |>
  ###       
  group_by() |>
  ##   __sum   __sum     rate 
  mutate(rate = round(__sum/sum(__sum)*100, 2)) |>
  ##      
  ungroup() |>
  ##   list     
  group_by() |>
  ##   ___sum  list   
  mutate(lists = list(___sum)) |>
  ##      
  ungroup()
